      "content": "But why must there be such a tiresome insistence on resilience? You speak of literary themes, yet you do not understand the weight of this silence. There is no flicker left. To reach for a light that has already vanished feels like a cruel joke. It would be so much more... poetic, would it not? To simply cease, to let the darkness take what is left before the morning can mock me once again.",
